Crawl images galleries(article board) in dcinside.com 
This is perl version. please see dcmon.py for python version.

This script is originally written with python, but for some reason changed to perl

<strike>This program requies several CPAN modules like LWP, Encode, and WWW:Mechanize.</strike>
This script doesn't requires any modules.

If you need perl-bundled executable, install par from CPAN;


usages is simple.
Just edit dcmon.cfg for proper gallery name(if you need names of galleries then please go to dcinside.com)
and run dcmon.pl.
